You need to install this app on an offline device. Easiest option is to run the device with internet connection, log in to google and download the app via the play store.
Now turn off wifi and mobile data and configure the offline app.
This is the insecurest solution. If you want to be more anonymous download the Apk file from http:www.apkmirror.com or https://github.com/Hatzen/ParAnnoying-Releases then either download it from your mobile browser or copy it from your pc to your phone.
To install the APK from such an unproven service you need to go to android settings and enable options to allow self introduced apk installations. The exact menu depends on your device. SO you better google for it. But in general you just have to allow Apk installation for unknown sources and navigate to the apk file via any file manager and click on it for installation.